{"tid":1468530,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班人真係痴左線，唔經大腦。","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:07:40.000Z","uid":263025,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d84d8322a979ea22c65aaf19021547e43a6d37dc","tid":1468530,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:51.000Z","msg":"其實你地企係機場目的係為左停機場運作。事實上今日有二百班機以上取消左，咁咪得lo. 打人，阻人，為乜？你地每一次行動，都有一個主線。今日個主線係企係度搞到你機場唔可以正常運行，人多有人多玩，人少有人少玩，人地著住撐警就圍咩玩法？<br />\n<br />\n我知大家都好嬲，我都好嬲，我不會割，我知你地好辛苦，覺得唔公平。係，係唔撚公平嫁啦宜家香港，我地唔係正正為左想香港公平d先企出黎咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果有人郁你，你就還拖，如果係公安，你想點就點，如果只係普通大陸人，佢無郁手，我地最多屌鳩佢。<br />\n<br />\n我地出黎佔機場目的係影響香港經濟，其他支線，大家忍下手。"},{"pid":"d8e1045488c463b884f331dcfec3b35f6330505b","tid":1468530,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/241gDjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F241gDjd.jpg&h=24184809&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3FpNcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3FpNcz.jpg&h=7d30142c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDEudSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDEudSz.jpg&h=51c08fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RW360xA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRW360xA.jpg&h=82f5ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyuYjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKyuYjf.jpg&h=abda31c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SqmDREf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqmDREf.jpg&h=86ba4115&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jUudSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jUudSB.jpg&h=7ccf2950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b950f274aa262a025932e62565c30e8adc80e50e","tid":1468530,"uid":123082,"like":0,